OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire: 'Nothing has
OL,4,Cchanged' since damning review says
OL,5,Cfirefighter
OL,7,FA serving firefighter has described
OL,8,Fhow he believes South Wales Fire and
OL,9,FRescue Service has not acted on the
OL,10,Ffindings of a damning review into its
OL,11,Fculture.
OL,13,F'Gareth', which is not his real name,
OL,14,Ftold ITV Cymru Wales that "things that
OL,15,Fhaven't been dealt with and the same
OL,16,Fold things on station are still being
OL,17,Fsaid".
OL,19,FHe said if issues continue at the
OL,20,Fscandal-hit service, it could pose a
OL,21,Frisk to the public's safety.
