OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire: 'Nothing has
OL,4,Cchanged' since damning review says
OL,5,Cfirefighter
OL,7,FIn January, a review into culture in
OL,8,FSouth Wales was published and included
OL,9,Fdetails of sexual harassment,
OL,10,Fmisogyny, racism and homophobia being
OL,11,Ftolerated at the service.
OL,13,FThe service told us it has been a
OL,14,F"difficult and unsettling time for our
OL,15,Fstaff", but it is "not complacent
OL,16,Fabout our Service's culture."
OL,18,F'It has just gone unchallenged for so
OL,19,Flong'
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/15
