OL,5,Cfirefighter
OL,7,F'Gareth' said when issues first came
OL,8,Fto light about bad behaviour at South
OL,9,FWales Fire, he was relieved that he
OL,10,Fwasn't alone in thinking there were
OL,11,Fproblems.
OL,13,FHe told us he had witnessed people
OL,14,Fmaking "racist jokes, racist comments
OL,15,Fabout people's skin, people's
OL,16,Freligion, people fleeing horrendous
OL,17,Fsituations."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/15
