OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire: 'Nothing has
OL,4,Cchanged' since damning review says
OL,5,Cfirefighter
OL,7,F"There was a story about someone in
OL,8,Fcharge of a watch who had taken the
OL,9,Fbrave step to come out as part of the
OL,10,FLGBTQ+ community", he said.
OL,12,F"Then a picture of their face was put
OL,13,Fon top of a Christmas tree fairy and
OL,14,Fthat was put on top of the Christmas
OL,15,Ftree. I can just imagine if you were
OL,16,Fpart of that community how that made
OL,17,Fyou feel and how you didn't think you
OL,18,Fwere accepted as part of South Wales
OL,19,FFire and Rescue Service."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/15
