OL,7,F'Gareth' said, "it's not something
OL,8,Fthat I thought I would have to contend
OL,9,Fwith joining a public service".
OL,11,F'A glimmer of hope that everything
OL,12,Fwould change'
OL,14,FWhen a review was announced into the
OL,15,Fculture at the service, 'Gareth' says
OL,16,Fhe was hopeful that it would lead to
OL,17,Fmeaningful change.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/15
