OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire: 'Nothing has
OL,4,Cchanged' since damning review says
OL,5,Cfirefighter
OL,7,FHe said he was "really excited for
OL,8,Fthis prospect of change. I knew a lot
OL,9,Fof people really didn't think that
OL,10,Fanything would come of the report but
OL,11,FI was one of those minority that
OL,12,Fthought: 'Yes, this is going to lead
OL,13,Fto something productive and useful and
OL,14,Fhelp us'."
OL,16,FWhen it was published in January 2024,
OL,17,Fthe review outlined a toxic culture
OL,18,Fand revealed allegations of sexism and
OL,19,Fabusive behaviour towards staff.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/15
