OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire: 'Nothing has
OL,4,Cchanged' since damning review says
OL,5,Cfirefighter
OL,7,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,8,Fsaid it was confident that the service
OL,9,Fwould "emerge with a more positive and
OL,10,Finclusive culture" as a result of the
OL,11,Freview.
OL,13,FHowever, more than eight months later,
OL,14,Ffrontline staff told us a very
OL,15,Fdifferent story. 'Gareth' says
OL,16,F"everything seems to have just not
OL,17,Fmoved along at all." He told us he is
OL,18,Flooking for ways to leave the fire
OL,19,Fservice. "Morale is really low, I
OL,20,Fdon't want to work there anymore".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/15
