OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire: 'Nothing has
OL,4,Cchanged' since damning review says
OL,5,Cfirefighter
OL,7,F"Nothing is happening, nothing is
OL,8,Fchanging. The same old things on
OL,9,Fstation are still being said, people
OL,10,Fare still gaining advantages because
OL,11,Fof people they know and I'm back to
OL,12,Fthe point where we were a year ago,
OL,13,Fwhere I'm just not proud anymore."
OL,15,F'That did nothing to reassure staff'
OL,17,FSome staff blame the appointment of a
OL,18,Fcontroversial interim fire chief for
OL,19,Fthe lack of progress at the service.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/15
