OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire: 'Nothing has
OL,4,Cchanged' since damning review says
OL,5,Cfirefighter
OL,7,FStuart Millington was brought in to
OL,8,Fsteady the ship after the publication
OL,9,Fof the damning cultural review.
OL,10,FHowever, days later ITV revealed he
OL,11,Fwas facing questions over his conduct.
OL,13,FThe former Welsh leader of the Fire
OL,14,FBrigades Union, Cerith Griffiths said,
OL,15,F"As soon I was told that he'd been
OL,16,Fgiven the interim appointment of Chief
OL,17,FFire Officer, I was really taken
OL,18,Faback."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/15
