OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire: 'Nothing has
OL,4,Cchanged' since damning review says
OL,5,Cfirefighter
OL,7,FIt emerged that Mr Millington was
OL,8,Ffacing an employment tribunal, accused
OL,9,Fof bullying and harassing a member of
OL,10,Fstaff whilst he was Assistant Chief
OL,11,FFire Officer at the North Wales
OL,12,FService.
OL,14,FMr Griffiths said, "That did
OL,15,Fabsolutely nothing to reassure staff
OL,16,Fthat things were going to change".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/15
