OL,7,FAn employment court has since struck
OL,8,Fout the case against Mr Millington
OL,9,Fafter it was argued the claimant
OL,10,Fsubmitted his complaint outside of the
OL,11,Flegal time limit.
OL,13,FMr Millington always denied the
OL,14,Fallegations and faces no further
OL,15,Faction.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/15
