OL,5,Cfirefighter
OL,7,FThe service told ITV Cymru Wales it
OL,8,F"will persist with making improvements
OL,9,Fto the culture of the Service with the
OL,10,Frecruitment of a new Chief Fire
OL,11,FOfficer who joins us later this year".
OL,13,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,14,Falso said, "Since publication of the
OL,15,Freport, transformation and change have
OL,16,Fbeen key priorities for the Service.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/15
