OL,5,Cfirefighter
OL,7,F'Gareth' wants to see change soon, but
OL,8,Fhe says without accountability, things
OL,9,Fcannot improve. "There needs to be a
OL,10,Fwider conversation about how we have
OL,11,Flet things get to this stage", he
OL,12,Fsaid, "and how do we go about learning
OL,13,Ffrom the mistakes of the past and
OL,14,Fmaking sure they are never repeated
OL,15,Fand no one ever has to suffer
OL,16,Funnecessarily again".
OL,18,FYou can hear more of Gareth's story on
OL,19,FWales This Week: Can our Fire Services
OL,20,Fbe Rescued? on Thursday 5th September
OL,21,Fat 8:30 pm on ITV Cymru Wales.
